quran[55]{c,v,t}:
  82,1,ﾄｰzessemaunfetaret
  82,2,Ve izelkevakibun teseret
  82,3,Ve izelbiharu fucciret
  82,4,Ve izelkuburu buﾂｴsiret
  82,5,ﾂｴAlimet nefsun ma kaddemet ve ahharet
  82,6,Ya eyyuhelﾂｴinsanu ma ﾄ歛rreke birabbikelkeriymi
  82,7,Elleziy halekake fesevvake feﾂｴadeleke
  82,8,Fiy eyyi suretin ma ﾅ歛e rekkebeke
  82,9,Kella bel tukezzibune biddiyni
  82,10,Ve inne ﾂｴaleykum lehafizﾄｱyne
  82,11,Kiramen katibiyne
  82,12,Yaﾂｴlemune ma tefﾂｴalune
  82,13,ﾄｰnnelﾂｴebrare lefiy naﾂｴﾄｱymin
  82,14,Ve innelfuccare lefiy cahﾄｱymin
  82,15,Yasleneha yevmeddiyni
  82,16,Ve ma hum ﾂｴanha biﾄ歛ibiyne
  82,17,Ve ma edrake ma yevmuddiyni
  82,18,Summe ma edrake ma yevmuddiyni
  82,19,Yevme la temliku nefun linefsin ﾅ歹yﾂｴen velﾂｴemru yevmeizin lillahi
  83,1,Veylun lilmutaffifiyne
  83,2,Elleziyne izektalu ﾂｴalennasi yestevfune
  83,3,Ve iza kaluhum ev vezenuhum yuhsirune
  83,4,Ela yezunnu ulaike ennehum mebﾂｴusune
  83,5,Liyevmin ﾂｴazﾄｱymin
  83,6,Yevme yekumunnasu lirabbilﾂｴalemiyne
  83,7,Kella inne kitabelfuccari lefiy sicciynin
  83,8,Ve ma edrake ma sicciynun
  83,9,Kitabun merkumun
  83,10,Veylun yevmeizin lilmukezzibiyne
  83,11,Elleziyne yukezzibune biyevmiddiyni
  83,12,Ve ma yukezzibu bihi illa kullu muﾂｴtedin esiymin
  83,13,ﾄｰza tutla aleyhi ayatuna kale esatﾄｱyrulﾂｴevveliyne
  83,14,Kella bel rane ﾂｴala kulubihim ma kanu yeksibune
  83,15,Kella innehum ﾂｴan rabbihim yevmeizin lemahcubune
  83,16,Summe innehum lesalulcahﾄｱymi
  83,17,Summe yukalu hazelleziy kuntum bihi tukezzibune
  83,18,Kella inne kitabelﾂｴebrari lefiy ﾂｴﾄｱlliyyiyne
  83,19,Ve ma edrake ma ﾂｴﾄｱlliyyune
  83,20,Kitabun merkumun
  83,21,Yeﾅ殄eduhulmukarrebune
  83,22,ﾄｰnnelebrare. Lefiy naﾂｴﾄｱymin
  83,23,ﾂｴAlelﾂｴeraiki yenzurune
  83,24,Taﾂｴrifu fiy vucuhihim nadretennaﾂｴﾄｱymi
  83,25,Yuskavne min rahﾄｱykﾄｱn mahtumin
  83,26,Hﾄｱtamuhu miskun ve fiy zalike felyetenafesilmutenasifune
  83,27,Ve mizacuhu min tesniymin
  83,28,Aynen yeﾅ殲ebu bihelmukarrebune
  83,29,ﾄｰnnelleziyne ecremu kanu minelleziyne amenu yadhakune
  83,30,Ve iza merru bihim yeteﾄ歛mezune
  83,31,Ve izenkalebu ila ehlihimunkalebu fekihiyne
  83,32,Ve iza reevhum kalu inne haulai ledallune
  83,33,Ve ma ursilu ﾂｴaleyhim hafizﾄｱyne
  83,34,Felyevmelleziyne amenu minelkuffari yadhakune
  83,35,ﾂｴAlelﾂｴeraiki yenzurune
  83,36,Hel suvvibelkuffaru ma kanu yefﾂｴalune